title: USD/JPY Risk Continues To Point Higher On Further Price Strength

USD/JPY Risk Continues To Point Higher On Further Price Strength

FXTechstrategy TeamForex 8 hours ago (Sep 17, 2019 11:31AM ET) By

www.investing.com/analysis/usdjpy-risk-continues-to-point-higher-on-further-price-strength-200465405 USD/JPY Risk Continues To Point Higher On Further Price Strength By By FXTechstrategy Team | 8 hours ago (Sep 17, 2019 11:31AM ET)

Follow risk continues to point higher on further price strength. On the upside, resistance comes in at 108.50 level. Above this level will turn attention to the 109.00 level. Further out, we expect a possible move toward the 109.50 level on a break of that area, A cut through here will open the door for more gain towards the 110.00. On the downside, support lies at the 107.50 level where a break will target the 107.00 level. Below that level will turn focus to the 106.50 level and then lower towards the 106.00 level. On the whole, USD/JPY faces further upside pressure in the days ahead.
